<Layout title="Music | Carson Smith">
    <Navbar />
    <main>
        <div class="text-white h-full px-5 flex md:flex-row flex-col mt-5 mb-5">
            <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-lg h-full flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-5">
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center md:text-left text-center text-blue-200 font-bold text-5xl">
                    Composing Orchestral Tracks For Your Indie Game Or Short Film
                </div>
                <div class="border-l-4 border-white h-full mx-5" />
                <div class="flex-1 flex items-center text-center md:text-right justify-center italic text-xl">
                    The importance of music within games and film cannot be emphasized enough. Original soundtracks are expertly crafted to be out of the way in the viewer's perspective until crucial momentsâ€”when they underscore pivotal moments and refine the emotions felt by the viewer.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full max-w-screen-lg justify-center mx-auto items-center mt-10">
            <div class="mx-auto flex-1 flex w-full justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-blue-200">
                Experience
            </div>
            <div class="indent-4 md:indent-8 text-white text-center flex-1 flex w-full justify-center text-xl">
                Since 2021 I've composed instrumental game tracks on-and-off for small developers on Roblox. I specialize in orchestral and instrumental tracks for a variety of musical roles in your game. I can compose for ambience, for action, and across a broad spectrum of emotions. I can compose music across a variety of Western historical styles, from 18th century baroque all the way to modern day orchestral work, and anything in between.
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 flex w-full mt-3 justify-center font-bold text-4xl text-blue-200">
                Works
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap5 mt-3">
